    Serializable

    public class BLEServiceProviderException
extends PaydiantException
    Represents exceptions that occurred during initialization & operations of BLE Service Providers. (i.e., DefaultBLEServiceProvider or custom IBLEServiceProvider implementation).

    4.9.0.1

        public static final int DEFAULT_BLE_LIBRARY_NOT_FOUND

        public static final int BLE_SERVICE_PROVIDER_LISTENER_NOT_SET
